This product includes software derived from / inspired by the upstream
Prometheus Node Exporter (https://github.com/prometheus/node_exporter),
Copyright The Prometheus Authors, licensed under the Apache License,
Version 2.0.

Metric names, label conventions, and CLI flag names follow that of the
upstream node_exporter so that existing Prometheus dashboards, alerting
rules, and deployment tooling continue to work unchanged.

This is the C++ sibling of merlion-node-exporter-rs
(https://github.com/MerlionOS/merlion-node-exporter-rs); the two
implementations are intentionally wire-compatible so operators can
swap one for the other without touching their Prometheus configuration.
